[
    {
        "text": "I'm speaking to 41-year-old Fumiyoshi Shimizu...",
        "startTime": 1445,
        "endTime": 4627,
        "slowStartTime": 2317,
        "slowEndTime": 7166
    },
    {
        "text": "...who has personally experienced how overwork can severely affect mental health.",
        "startTime": 4767,
        "endTime": 10383,
        "slowStartTime": 7300,
        "slowEndTime": 15799
    },
    {
        "text": "Fourteen years ago, Shimizu-san was one of the 800,000 workers...",
        "startTime": 12229,
        "endTime": 16958,
        "slowStartTime": 18493,
        "slowEndTime": 25662
    },
    {
        "text": "...employed at convenience store chains across Japan.",
        "startTime": 17037,
        "endTime": 20393,
        "slowStartTime": 25706,
        "slowEndTime": 30814
    },
    {
        "text": "Because of punishing schedules and general labor shortages across Japan,...",
        "startTime": 21404,
        "endTime": 25720,
        "slowStartTime": 32256,
        "slowEndTime": 38805
    },
    {
        "text": "...24-hour stores are difficult to staff.",
        "startTime": 26245,
        "endTime": 29105,
        "slowStartTime": 39517,
        "slowEndTime": 43882
    },
    {
        "text": "Shimizu-san's dedication to his job reminds me of a pervasive Japanese phrase,...",
        "startTime": 29840,
        "endTime": 35115,
        "slowStartTime": 44910,
        "slowEndTime": 52897
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"ganbaru\" or \"to persevere through hardship.\"",
        "startTime": 36217,
        "endTime": 39541,
        "slowStartTime": 54475,
        "slowEndTime": 59537
    },
    {
        "text": "But persevering on just three hours of sleep a day...",
        "startTime": 40585,
        "endTime": 43872,
        "slowStartTime": 61028,
        "slowEndTime": 66033
    },
    {
        "text": "...puts the body and the brain under enormous stress.",
        "startTime": 44165,
        "endTime": 47335,
        "slowStartTime": 66397,
        "slowEndTime": 71228
    },
    {
        "text": "A year into the job, Shimizu-san was diagnosed with depression,...",
        "startTime": 48377,
        "endTime": 52413,
        "slowStartTime": 72715,
        "slowEndTime": 78845
    },
    {
        "text": "...but he ignored his doctor's advice to take a break.",
        "startTime": 52826,
        "endTime": 55996,
        "slowStartTime": 79389,
        "slowEndTime": 84219
    },
    {
        "text": "For better or for worse, there's a deeply ingrained mentality in Japanese society...",
        "startTime": 56661,
        "endTime": 61751,
        "slowStartTime": 85142,
        "slowEndTime": 92851
    },
    {
        "text": "...that the group comes before the needs of the individual.",
        "startTime": 62047,
        "endTime": 65217,
        "slowStartTime": 93221,
        "slowEndTime": 98050
    },
    {
        "text": "Because Shimizu-san was put on unpaid leave,...",
        "startTime": 66411,
        "endTime": 69086,
        "slowStartTime": 99767,
        "slowEndTime": 103854
    },
    {
        "text": "...he asked the company to compensate him for his overtime hours.",
        "startTime": 69396,
        "endTime": 73031,
        "slowStartTime": 104244,
        "slowEndTime": 109771
    },
    {
        "text": "Shimizu-san took the company to court and won.",
        "startTime": 73324,
        "endTime": 78248,
        "slowStartTime": 110136,
        "slowEndTime": 117597
    },
    {
        "text": "Shimizu-san was awarded 15,000 US dollars in compensation for his overtime hours...",
        "startTime": 85600,
        "endTime": 91886,
        "slowStartTime": 128550,
        "slowEndTime": 138054
    },
    {
        "text": "...and for the damage the work had done to his health,...",
        "startTime": 92219,
        "endTime": 95111,
        "slowStartTime": 138479,
        "slowEndTime": 142892
    },
    {
        "text": "...a rare outcome in Japan.",
        "startTime": 95799,
        "endTime": 97754,
        "slowStartTime": 143849,
        "slowEndTime": 146856
    }
]